info.title: SpecialWords
info.description:
Scenarios to verify that reserved words can be used in service and generators will handle it appropriately.

Current list of special words
```txt
and
as
assert
async
await
break
class
constructor
continue
def
del
elif
else
except
exec
finally
for
from
global
if
import
in
is
lambda
not
or
pass
raise
return
try
while
with
yield
```
